uriMetadata.description:
Yaribel the Whale 

Customise · Digitise · Equalise 
OnChain Whales NFTs, have created an NFT family, where users can express their creativity in an immutable form. Developing a system where investors determine the aesthetics and value of NFT art, bringing forward a new era of decentralisation. 
This excitement and individualism is also rewarded with bountiful utility, visit the website to learn more. 

Investors may opt to burn any combination of their collection to redeem a complete NFToken that mimics their design. Creating a deflationary collection of NFTs, that are redeemed for unique, holder created, artwork. 

Beauty is in the eye of the beholder, and you have a chance to make your beauty. 

**NONE OF THESE IMAGES WILL EVER BE SOLD OR RETAIN VALUE**
